description: That one used to snort percocets and run into the back of cars on the 405 freeway, outside of Los Angeles in rush hour. She had these gloves with tiny nails poked into the skin, designed to lightly wound the skin - they would eventually pay her for that pleasure. She told you that you were a good boy, when you came on the asphalt in the alley behind the bar.
name: Rave Concubine
